</code></pre>
Might have made that more clear... but .forEach is an ES5 addition...<p>Given the backlash with ES6, I wonder why we didn&#x27;t see this with ES5... &quot;OMG they added extra sugar to Array.prototype, we&#x27;re all gonna die!&quot;
